paper_metadata.title: MAIN TEXT
paper_metadata.extraction_summary: The paper discusses the inhibition of hERG channels by sarizotan, focusing on the KCNH2 gene. No specific genetic variants in KCNH2 were reported.

challenges: The paper did not report any specific genetic variants in the KCNH2 gene.
extraction_metadata.notes: The paper focused on the functional effects of sarizotan on hERG channels without detailing specific genetic variants in KCNH2.
